{"tid":1887088,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"富臨集團 20間餐館休業 ！","createTime":"2020-02-19T10:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T10:38:02.000Z","uid":319512,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"42dd2dad3e4979a9391c661e36cedc8f08e4531d","tid":1887088,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n富臨集團宣布，因應新型肺炎疫情令市民減少外出用膳，管理層在審慎考慮後，決定旗下約20間餐館短暫休業，進行徹底清潔和消毒。<br />\n<br />\n而因應營業店舖減少，前線員工本月需按既定程序，安排放3天無薪假期，受影響員工約2000名，但強調現時未有裁員計劃。<br />\n<br />\n另外，公司指，疫情進一步打擊零售餐飲市道，集團跟大部部業主磋商租金紓緩措施，並推行一系列營運成本控制方案，包括本月內下調全體執行董事薪酬50%、下調高級管理層薪酬20%，作為降低成本的第一步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509498-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509498-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5EKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=108cc9ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509498-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9d93fd97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509498-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"57a69eba106be96d957e24fce593d5b3bb3c80b8","tid":1887088,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"無良僱主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244062f2dd3642f48511e2cf0855441882e4ac18","tid":1887088,"uid":36004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:05:49.000Z","msg":"又派成績表 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd10a772ad0d7018e29df471bb59a78ec7520b86","tid":1887088,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"